OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FPolls have closed in England,
OL,7,FScotland, and Wales in one of the
OL,8,Flargest elections the UK has seen
OL,9,Foutside of a national general election.
OL,11,FAt the closing of polls, Ofcom
OL,12,Frestrictions on what broadcasters can
OL,13,Fand cannot speak about were lifted,
OL,14,Fand the UK media became free to speak
OL,15,Fabout election issues, polls, and
OL,16,Fpredictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
