OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FThe results of these elections are
OL,7,Flikely to dominate news coverage for
OL,8,Fsome time, as voters look set to
OL,9,Freject the UK's dominate two party
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FBut what's at stake, and how soon will
OL,13,Fyou know the results?
OL,15,FPolling day
OL,17,FPolitical leaders were photographed in
OL,18,Ftheir own constituencies casting their
OL,19,Fvotes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
