OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778242270
OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski cast
OL,7,Fhis own ballot by post and accompanied
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Green leader Anthony
OL,9,FSlaughter to his polling station in
OL,10,FPenarth.
OL,12,FThe key stories to look out for:
OL,14,FThere are several themes to look out
OL,15,Ffor across the UK as results begin to
OL,16,Fcome in, more broadly, however, they
OL,17,Ftell a story of the UK rejecting its
OL,18,Ftraditional two-party system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
