OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FAcross England, Labour faces losing
OL,7,Fvotes to both Reform on the right and
OL,8,Fthe Greens on the left, whilst the
OL,9,FConservatives face a squeeze from
OL,10,FReform on their right and the Lib Dems
OL,11,Fto their left.
OL,13,FWhile governing parties typically
OL,14,Fperform less well at local elections,
OL,15,Fa rejection of Labour at the local
OL,16,Flevel will be spun by the prime
OL,17,Fminister's political opponents as a
OL,18,Fdamning indictment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
