OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FDespite the expectation management
OL,7,Ffrom political parties hoping to take
OL,8,Fthe edge of large defeats, depending
OL,9,Fon the scale of these losses, the
OL,10,Ffollowing days could see renewed
OL,11,Fpressure and scrutiny on Starmer, and
OL,12,Feven Kemi Badenoch's leadership.
OL,14,FWhen will you know results?
OL,16,FUnlike in general elections, there is
OL,17,Fno reliable exit poll for the English
OL,18,Flocal elections, or the national
OL,19,Fcontests in Scotland and Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
