OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FIn nationwide contests, broadcasters
OL,7,Ftypically club together to pay for and
OL,8,Fcommission an exit poll asking voters
OL,9,Fhow they cast their ballot when they
OL,10,Fleave the poling station.
OL,12,FThese can be incredibly accurate but
OL,13,Falso cost a lot of money.
OL,15,FIt is not believed any such reliable
OL,16,Fpolls have been commissioned ahead of
OL,17,Fthese election's results.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
