OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FThe first results are expected to
OL,7,Fstart arriving overnight, as 47
OL,8,FEnglish councils plan to count and
OL,9,Fdeclare the winners into the early
OL,10,Fhours of the morning.
OL,12,FThe majority of counts will begin
OL,13,Fdeclaring on Friday, however, with the
OL,14,Fresults in Scotland, Wales, and the
OL,15,Fremaining English councils and
OL,16,Fmayoralties expected after 12 pm.
OL,18,FFour councils expect to announce
OL,19,Fresults on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
