OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWill early results show any signs of
OL,12,Fthe bigger picture?
OL,14,FThe results coming in overnight into
OL,15,FFriday are just a small snapshot of a
OL,16,Fmuch wider picture.
OL,18,FThough not enough to determine wider
OL,19,Fthemes, they could give early signs of
OL,20,Feach party's fortunes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
