OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FThe Greens hope to perform well in
OL,7,FLondon, taking control of several
OL,8,Fcouncils from Labour.
OL,10,FEaling, which is currently controlled
OL,11,Fby Labour, could be one area where the
OL,12,FGreens do well. That result is
OL,13,Fexpected at 4.30 am and could be a
OL,14,Fsign of how well Zack Polanski's party
OL,15,Fcan expect to do across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
