OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FEarly signs of how many votes the
OL,7,FTories have lost to Reform could come
OL,8,Ffrom Hampshire, Kensington and
OL,9,FChelsea, and Harlow, all of which are
OL,10,Fcurrently controlled by Kemi
OL,11,FBadenoch's party and expect to declare
OL,12,Ftheir results overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
