OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FITV News understands the Lib Dems
OL,7,Fexpect to see their best results after
OL,8,F4pm on Friday, but an early indicator
OL,9,Fcould come from both Sutton, and
OL,10,FRichmond who both expect to declare
OL,11,Fovernight. Sir Ed Davey's party also
OL,12,Fhopes to perform well in Merton, which
OL,13,Fis currently controlled by Labour and
OL,14,Fis electing all of its 57 councillors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
