OL,3,CPolls close in an election that could
OL,4,Cshape politics for some time
OL,6,FA sign of how much Reform have
OL,7,Fsqueezed Labour by could be seen
OL,8,Ffurther North in Wigan and Oldham,
OL,9,Fwhich expect to declare in the early
OL,10,Fhours of Friday morning. Angela
OL,11,FRayner's council of Tameside, which is
OL,12,Fcurrently controlled by Labour could
OL,13,Fbe another sign of Labour's looming
OL,14,Felection defeat.
